C\-RET \(dqConfirm\(dq %{{confirm}}

.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Modifiers
.sp
Zero or more modifiers can precede a key.
.TS
box center;
l|l.
T{
Modifier
T}	T{
wks form
T}
_
T{
Control
T}	T{
\fBC\-\fP
T}
_
T{
Meta/Alt
T}	T{
\fBM\-\fP
T}
_
T{
Hyper/Super
T}	T{
\fBH\-\fP
T}
_
